<li>Log File Information: When you visit pornbox.video, our servers may automatically record certain information that your web browser sends such as your web request, IP address, browser type, browser language, referring URL, platform type, domain names and the date and time of your request.</li>
<li>Emails: If you contact us, we may keep a record of that correspondence.</li>
